						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the wall of the backyard of Hire-maṭha.</p>						

						<p>Circa 16th century.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land in Hūvinahaḍagile to Narahari-bhaṭṭa, son of Chimmarasa, of Viśvāmitra-<hi rend="italic">gōtra</hi> and Ṛik-<hi rend="italic">śākhā.</hi> </p>						

