<p>
<lb n="1"/><unclear>ko</unclear>ṁḍakuraciya rukkuśākha <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>ya viśvāmitragōtrada ciṁ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>marasa Ayiyanavara makkaḷu
<lb n="4"/>naraharibhaṭṭarige hūvinahaḍagi
<lb n="5" break="no"/>leya grāmadalu kārajōḷagada bī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>javari sarvvamāṁnyada vritti <unclear>voṁ</unclear>dakaṁ
<lb n="7"/>ghaṁṭeya pahara <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> koṭṭa dharmmavanu
<lb n="8"/>Āru pālisidavaru gaṁgeya taḍiyoḷu
<lb n="9"/>sāvira kavileyaṁ brāhmarige dānavanu ko
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṭṭaru <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> Āru Aḷupidavaru gaṁ
<lb n="11" break="no"/>geya taḍiyalu sāvirakavileya va
<lb n="12" break="no"/>dhisida pāpavanu EIduvaru Akṣayasukhadī dharmmava
<lb n="13"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> si rakṣisida puṁṇyapuruṣarggellaṁ bhakṣisi
<lb n="14"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tanasa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
